Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:21.22,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:26.85,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.81,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.69,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.79,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:50.17,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:57.05,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:03.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:12.66,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.86,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:20.91,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.95,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:29.48,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokyo Cup entry trials\Nare in two weeks already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,2000)}To get you in shape for the fall season\Nwe'll need special practices.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.83,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(2000,0)}We only have two weeks for everything\Nso get used to the intense schedule starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintaining the shrine is finished, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means... That Todo too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I freed him from the shrine in advance, \Nso while preparing for a flight to America, he won't have to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo's departure date has finally been fixed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the day after tomorrow, as a matter of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we don't have a lot of time, \Nbut I was thinking of some kind of celebration for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Oka has already supported this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Yeah... Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still believe Todo is making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming a pro without anyone's patronage \Nimpoverishes you with accommodation and entry fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason why one should find a sponsor first, \Nand think of a further career afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, all the local sponsors were rejected by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The national championship made him famous.\NEven the tennis association itself noticed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be participating \Nin American tournaments eventually anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he chose his own path, the thorny one indeed.\NStarting a career with zero support is always challenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the reason, by any chance, Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a reckless pilgrim,\Nhe sticks to this meaningless path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is trying to take this hobby away from him. \NWhat drives him to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess \Nit's his sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One man once convinced him \Nto pursue this goal dedicatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? \NAnd who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,100,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HE3C4A2&\t(0,1100,\bord0.11\blur0.4\3c&H945431&)\c&HF7EEF0&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\an8\fscx167\fscy157}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get to the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer is almost over, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo... \NI wonder if he'll be already home by winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our troublesome friend\Nis leaving Japan after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that going abroad \Nis something special these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, we better get used \Nto no longer seeing each other frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, today we are sending Todo off appropriately.\NNo ceremonies, no loud mournings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So that he could know for sure, \Nhe won't make anyone sad by leaving or not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty much the reason why \NI decided to fix up that dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, to your future success, \Nwe are raising this sixty-third vintage Château Burgundy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At least once a week, \Nmake contact with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ozaki.\NTodo is not some kind of child anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you'll be happy there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you'll be suffering,\Nanyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Always make contact with us. \NWhenever you see an opportunity to contact us, use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that after leaving \Nyou might forget we'll be by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't be worried. As long as you keep in touch with us, \Nno matter what, I won't be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your point, Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, let me give you one last trip advice: \Nyou shouldn't be trying to become the second Mr. Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are you only. And not the Munakata Jin reincarnation. \NYou are our friend Todo Takayuki. Let it remain that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we appreciate you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Munakata... has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not die...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He has died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you,\Nthough I'm not sure you need it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I still believe you're making \Nthe biggest mistake of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say a word this evening, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you with Todo have a lot to say to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No... You know, actually... Actually, I have nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, sure, sure! Nothing at all, sure! \NWell, Todo. She is all yours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad that Todo is building his future... \NThe happiness of a person should be above others' opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And since Todo chose this path himself, I'm sure \Nthat I'll be happy as well, along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, only one waypoint left, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This autumn, another Tokyo Cup is being held. \NHave you already applied for it, Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am participating in entry matches too. \NLet's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! I forgot to ask \Nhis tomorrow's plane departure time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Todo!\NDon't you feel the need to call your beloved one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seemed to me you couldn't talk in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any "beloved ones".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even being twenty-one years old, you still deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo's love now belongs to tennis only. \NAfter all, Munakata Jin's ghost possesses him currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are exaggerating...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Denying everything like some school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think everyone should have \Nfifty-six ex-lovers as you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten of them, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally unfair! Am I not handsome? \NI don't have a single one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then... \NMay we start moving to exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Todo. I'll pick you up tomorrow, \Nmake sure you won't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something else... \NOka, what I wanted to tell you... But I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Definitely... I'm sure!\NTodo will definitely find a way to let me know about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late. \NShe must be sleeping already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening. \NI'm listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm listening. Is that you, Todo?\NI'm so happy you decided to call.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your plane tomorrow... What time does it take off?\NJust once more... Even for a second... I want to see you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want you to perceive me as a child...\NI don't want anyone to perceive me as a child!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oka Hiromi. Nineteen years old.\NI know that falling in love is nothing extraordinary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the ecstatic desire to see someone \Nis nothing extraordinary either! But still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, it seems that's just the way love is, \Nand I can't help it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to get in the way of the person I love... \NI won't let my feelings take control of me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be an obstacle... \NI won't let myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand that whatever your plan is,\NI'm not the part of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, the last thing I want to interrupt is your plans. \NAnd yet, there's nothing I can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before it starts to snow, \Nwe won't meet again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are the ones...\NThe flowers I gave to Todo yesterday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,20,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Dear Oka, \Nat 20:15 I am departing from Narita \Nwith flight 522\NT.T
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Oka,\Nat 20:15, I am departing from Narita Airport with flight 522.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings. \NSorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind, it's fine. I benefit from alternating \Ntraining with real matches too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! You will play a three-set match with Ryuzaki! \NShe has kindly agreed to prepare you for the qualifiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's so unfortunate! \NI have to hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick to the baseline!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get there by 20:15, \NI have to leave the court not later than at five!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get into position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, you better relax, \Nbut don't loosen off completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I'm ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy with practice again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I'll forget Hiromi's face soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When does your Saturday practice end?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think... At five PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Let's go have fun after then! \NI got us a couple of tickets for the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What else? \NDon't tell me you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to prepare for the Autumn Tokyo Cup, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura forces you to come up with a strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What else did I expect... \NYou both always go all-out on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense, I'm just an outsider. \NI'll never understand a real player you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NHiromi has to play soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't go to the sea.\NHas anything happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a thing... Nothing worth mentioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki... Get yourself together! \NNext time I will indubitably go! You got my word!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But today... Forgive me. \NI'm extraordinarily busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis is more important, \NI understand, don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Game for Ryuzaki! Game count: 6-1!\NSet count: 1-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, we are equal, \Nbut today you kinda half a step behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm out of shape right now, \NI was able to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still unsure \Nyou'll be able to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'll be able to conquer the world, \NI'm not sure as well. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that my friend \Napplied himself to something with full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all the doubts and condemnation, \Nhe found the courage to go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even being the only one who thinks this way, \NI will not give that belief up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some might say it is embarrassing and stupid - \Nto pursue your dream with such a burning passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That proves that the one who is being criticized \Nshould be supported with burning passion as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They will repeat "Won't work, won't happen," \Nand that now's the entr'acte of your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...shutting up once you start to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You romanticize things too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this only because Munakata Jin, \Nin my spot, would have done the same. And will always be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Out! The second set score is 5-1! \NRyuzaki lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad! If I continue \Nfinishing every game with an out, I'll lose the match!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, if I start taking it seriously, \NI might leave the court too late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The flight is at 20:15. \NIf I go now, I can still get there on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, please... \NWait for me just a little longer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! What are you waiting for? \NIt's your service now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still... \NI must do my best whatsoever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm playing against Madame Butterfly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I lose to her on purpose...\NI won't forgive myself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Familiar voice. We need your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotcha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving for New York with flight 522?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave luggage here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We arrived early, so there's a lot of time. \NLet's find where to spend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Game count: 7-5!\NSet count: 2-0! Winner - Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After such a long break, it was a pleasure \Nto see Hiromi rushing to fight as furiously as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You started the second set with losing 5 to 1.\NBut you managed to make it 7-5 eventually. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, enough for today! \NDismissed, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I get there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I still get there in time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight 522 to New York passengers \Nmay now begin their boarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame, exactly when do you need to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it's 20:15!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unpleasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. Gotta get there in time first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a spicy story! I truly hope you find your happiness \Nwith a foreign guy, but how spicy it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be sad if your foreign boyfriend \Nleaves without you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll get you there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:20:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Passengers of the plane 522 to New York, \Nleaving at 20:15, are requested to proceed to the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The sixty-third gate of our airport is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Todo. You better be heading to exit now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more...\NThere's still some coffee left in my cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Todo!\NWhat's with that sudden attitude of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been... \NPlaying with Madame Butterfly at today's training!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,6-1, 7-5, and I lost both sets. \NBut you know, this time I was already close to winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one step... No! \NOne half a step was separating me from victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say so, I believe. \NThis full step, or half a step, is within your capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo... I really... Love you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aikawa Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo has left for New York\Nand Hiromi feels very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, alright? Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokyo Cup match is coming at us imminently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Todo is away, he'll surely do his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when the game day comes,\NHiromi is still acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.63,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hiromi?\NHas something happened to Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "I want to see you, Todo..."